---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About — ajscanlan.dev" description="Working notebook — engineering, writing, and the space between.">
    <div class="layout-post pt-16 pb-20">

        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 font-mono text-2xs uppercase tracking-eyebrow text-ink-400 mb-4">
            <span class="size-1.5 rounded-full bg-green shrink-0"></span>
            Available for new roles · Jun 2026
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-ink-900 mt-0 mb-4">A.J. Scanlan</h1>

        <p class="text-base text-ink-600 max-w-prose-narrow mt-0 mb-8">
            Senior software engineer. I build reliable systems, write clearly about how they work,
            and bring the same rigor to both. Based in NYC.
        </p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-[140px_1fr] gap-x-10 gap-y-0 border-t border-ink-100 max-[640px]:grid-cols-1">
            <span class="font-mono text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-eyebrow text-ink-400 py-4 border-b border-ink-100 self-start max-[640px]:pb-1 max-[640px]:border-b-0">Currently</span>
            <span class="text-sm text-ink-700 py-4 border-b border-ink-100">Open to senior IC and tech-lead roles — distributed systems, developer tooling, or product engineering at a company doing something that matters.</span>

            <span class="font-mono text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-eyebrow text-ink-400 py-4 border-b border-ink-100 self-start max-[640px]:pb-1 max-[640px]:border-b-0">Background</span>
            <span class="text-sm text-ink-700 py-4 border-b border-ink-100">Mobile engineer turned full-stack. Spent several years building production iOS apps, then shifted toward TypeScript, distributed systems, and platform work. I care about correctness, legibility, and shipping.</span>

            <span class="font-mono text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-eyebrow text-ink-400 py-4 border-b border-ink-100 self-start max-[640px]:pb-1 max-[640px]:border-b-0">How I work</span>
            <span class="text-sm text-ink-700 py-4 border-b border-ink-100">Prefer async, written communication. Ship iteratively, document why not just what, and flag risks early. I've worked in small startups and larger product teams — I adapt, but I write and read a lot either way.</span>

            <span class="font-mono text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-eyebrow text-ink-400 py-4 border-b border-ink-100 self-start max-[640px]:pb-1 max-[640px]:border-b-0">Stack</span>
            <span class="text-sm text-ink-700 py-4 border-b border-ink-100 flex flex-wrap gap-1 items-start">
                <span class="font-mono text-xs rounded py-0.5 px-2 inline-block bg-ink-900 text-paper-100">TypeScript</span>
                <span class="font-mono text-xs rounded py-0.5 px-2 inline-block bg-ink-900 text-paper-100">React</span>
                <span class="font-mono text-xs rounded py-0.5 px-2 inline-block bg-ink-900 text-paper-100">Astro</span>
                <span class="font-mono text-xs rounded py-0.5 px-2 inline-block bg-ink-900 text-paper-100">Swift</span>
                <span class="font-mono text-xs rounded py-0.5 px-2 inline-block bg-paper-200 text-ink-600">Python</span>
                <span class="font-mono text-xs rounded py-0.5 px-2 inline-block bg-paper-200 text-ink-600">PostgreSQL</span>
                <span class="font-mono text-xs rounded py-0.5 px-2 inline-block bg-paper-200 text-ink-600">Node</span>
            </span>

            <span class="font-mono text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-eyebrow text-ink-400 py-4 border-b border-ink-100 self-start max-[640px]:pb-1 max-[640px]:border-b-0">Reach me</span>
            <span class="text-sm text-ink-700 py-4 border-b border-ink-100">
                <a href="mailto:hi@ajscanlan.dev" class="text-ink-900 no-underline border-b border-ink-200 hover:text-fox-ink hover:border-fox-ink">hi@ajscanlan.dev</a>
                <span class="mx-1.5 text-ink-300">·</span>
                <a href="https://github.com/AJScanlan" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-ink-900 no-underline border-b border-ink-200 hover:text-fox-ink hover:border-fox-ink">GitHub</a>
            </span>

            <span class="font-mono text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-eyebrow text-ink-400 py-4 border-b border-ink-100 self-start max-[640px]:pb-1 max-[640px]:border-b-0">This site</span>
            <span class="text-sm text-ink-700 py-4 border-b border-ink-100">Astro 5 · TypeScript · Tailwind · MDX · hosted on Vercel</span>
        </div>

    </div>
</BaseLayout>
